docs {
  ## Get Deposit Contract

  Retrieve the address and chain ID of the deposit contract used by the beacon chain.

  ### Response (200)
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "chain_id": "1",
      "address": "0x00000000219ab540356cBB839Cbe05303d7705Fa"
    }
  }
  ```
}
